A '''rheostat''' was an internal device on [[Droid/Legends|droids]] that regulated internal heat. When [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] were [[Scout/Legends|scouting]] the ice [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] suggested that they turn up their rheostats to keep from freezing solid.

